Frequently Asked Questions for Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V. (NYSE:BSMX)
What is Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V.'s stock symbol?

Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V. trades on the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE) under the ticker symbol "BSMX."



How often does Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V. pay dividends? What is the dividend yield for Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V.?

Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V. declared a  dividend on Friday, May 19th. Investors of record on Monday, May 29th will be given a dividend of $0.165 per share on Tuesday, June 6th. The ex-dividend date is Wednesday, May 24th. This is a positive change from Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V.'s previous  dividend of $0.13.  View Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V.'s Dividend History.



How were Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V.'s earnings last quarter?

Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V. (NYSE:BSMX) announced its quarterly earnings results on Thursday, October, 29th. The company reported $0.16 earnings per share for the quarter, missing the consensus estimate of $0.17 by $0.01. The business earned $884.26 million during the quarter, compared to the consensus estimate of $1.02 billion. Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V. had a return on equity of 14.09% and a net margin of 16.29%.  View Grupo Financiero Santander Mexico S.A. B. de C.V.'s Earnings History.



