Company Description                    




                        Grupo Financiero Santander S.A.B. de C.V. is a Mexican holding company that offers a wide range of financial services. These include retail and commercial banking, securities brokerage, financial advisory and other type of investment services. The group was founded in 1997 when the Spanish bank Banco Santander S.A. acquired the financial group "Grupo Financiero Invermexico" (founded in 1991) and changed its name to "Grupo Financiero Santander Mexicano".                      


